name: PIM_Inhaled_Corticosteroids_ICS
title: PIM_Inhaled_Corticosteroids_(ICS)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Inhaled corticosteroids: Used to identify all inhalation medications that include corticosteroids and combinations preparations.),(Data Element Scope: DRUG_CLASS_MEMBERS: PHARMACOLOGIC),(Inclusion Criteria: All inhaled preparations, both nasal and oral),(Exclusion Criteria: (1) TTY in {DF, DFG}. (2) Specifies route other than inhaled. No combination RxNORM's.)
